text: Tamim Al-Dawsari (, born 4 June 1989) is a Saudi Arabian professional footballer who plays as a winger for Al-Nahda. ==Career== Al-Dawsari began his career at the youth team of Al-Nassr. Al-Dawsari joined with Al-Qala in 2008 To participate in the playoffs Saudi Third Division . and joined with Al- Shabab in 2010 On 14 January 2014, Al-Dawsari joined side Al-Shoulla on loan for the 2013–14 season . On 25 August 2014, Al-Dawsari left Al-Shabab and signed a one-year contract with Al-Shoulla . On 16 January 2015, Al-Dawsari left Al-Shoulla and signed a tow-year contract with Al-Raed. On 16 October 2016 , Al-Dawsari signed contract with Al-Kawkab. ==References== == External links == * Category:1989 births Category:Living people Category:Saudi Arabian footballers Category:Saudi Arabia youth international footballers Category:Al- Nassr FC players Category:Al-Qala Club players Category:Al-Shabab FC (Riyadh) players Category:Al-Shoulla FC players Category:Al-Raed FC players Category:Al-Kawkab FC players Category:Al-Nahda Club (Saudi Arabia) players Category:Saudi Professional League players Category:Prince Mohammad bin Salman League players Category:Saudi Second Division players Category:Saudi Third Division Players Category:Association football wingers
